{"type": "article", "id": 32010, "title": "Nike Lab推出秋冬系列，以及，蕾哈娜首个Fenty Puma 系列发售 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-09T02:26:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2871, "name": "Apple Watch"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 32594, "name": "NikeLab Essentials"}, {"id": 32595, "name": "Dime"}, {"id": 32596, "name": "TPP"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 15558, "name": "Vince"}, {"id": 32597, "name": "niko and…"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160909095800I6ADg0RVe4CJ1Bdv.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/government-trade/wal-mart-gap-j-c-penney-macys-tpp-10526741/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国零售商及品牌公司联名要求美国政府于今年加入 TPP 协议</b></a> | 包括 Gap、Adidas、梅西百货、Michael Kors、Under Armour 在内的多个美国时尚品牌及零售商，集体向白宫和众议院写信要求美国政府于今年加入 TPP 协议。 TPP 即跨太平洋伙伴关系协定（Trans-Pacific Partnership Agreement），也被称作“经济北约”。成员国之间会带来产品、服务价格下降，物流速度增加，各国可以取长补短，消费者是最直接的受益者之一。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/financial/vince-narrowed-q2-loss-bested-wall-street-eps-estimate-contemporary-fashion-apparel-10527088/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国 Vince 服装集团第二季度亏损继续</b></a>  | Vince 在第二季度净亏损 200 万美元。净营业额下降了 24.1%，至 6070 万美元。而此前华尔街预测其净营业额为 6420 万美元。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/macys-apple-herald-square-new-york-10525170/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅西百货将在其商场内开设 Apple 旗舰店</b></a> | 梅西百货将在它位于 Herald 广场的纽约旗舰店内开设它的第一个 Apple 店。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/tommy-bahama-canada-doug-wood-sherway-gardens-toronto-calgary-10525787/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国休闲服装品牌&nbsp;Tommy Bahama 将加拿大市场作为其增长的推动力</a></b> | 三年前 Tommy Bahama 从 Jaytex 拿到加拿大营业许可后，这个品牌在多伦多 CF Sherway Gardens 开设了一家占地约为 325 平方米的加拿大的第二大分店。&nbsp;<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/nikelab-essentials-2016-second-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">NikeLab Essentials 推出 2016 秋冬系列</a>，以简约风格呈现了多款不同色调的男女装。该系列已上架 Nike 官网。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091122rBJszISxDNouj4OH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091122ExCPHQzktpa7jgFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091122RMNPqnk5OfVKilWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091123nKv4qlhWaE6sZzX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091123o9IC27MLl4pVs1xT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609090911234TP50ljiXCRg281D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091134gwC4PQkMds9Auojl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091135eYs6NmC3vRa1H2fy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091135o4uvMEfGstT6QacX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本生活方式集合店 niko and… 与美式经典品牌 Champion 合作推出棉质<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/champion-x-niko-and-reverse-weave\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Reverse Weave 系列</a>。强调简约、休闲的生活品味。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091148W8E5CD7hLzIlpv4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609090911488kcbugFq7XQRYnj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091148GNI25VTgJqB7UXZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091159dsl9KAHPm63I4z0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090909115919cFv3ZBX2NJ8AtD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091159P8pFMy0fjcxmVqA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>随着 Apple 发布会上 Apple Watch Series 2 正式公布，合作款式 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/apple-watch-hermes-2016-series-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apple Watch Hermès </a>也推出了全新色系及款式。全套系列包含表壳和表带定价为  1149 至 1499 美元。另购表带定价为 339 至 689 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091213gdVzEFX2CMhWk46A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091223xfZ0OgYhQWwoy7S4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091223lDtzr0RVQ1wuOkTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091223lkURqIY3AMBngfOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091232d6Al0Ie8JfB7trG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091239fzVAb0ojaw5gDy7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091239VfHyMIO6CdlPijxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/rihanna-fenty-puma-clothing-buy/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 的首个 Fenty Puma 系列已于官方网店及指定门店进行发售</a>。受日本街头文化的启发，Rihanna 在这个系列中以黑、白为主色，大玩日本元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091307THsiCQlwjcaFo4pf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091307SpbZi7OTfUExhkKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091307v5GApNP7weLKT4QS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609090913154UGM6nEej9RWHOfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091315mUIDZWuVbkOry6xM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091315zrtlMawQXfAZpG9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091322jM2UOF04plobIfB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">时隔一年，Vans 与加拿大滑板品牌 Dime 再度合作，带来全新的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/vans-x-dime-old-skool-pro-fairlane\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Old Skool Pro 与 Fairlane 鞋款</a>。这个全新的联名系列将于 9 月 17 日登陆 Supreme 与全球各大 Vans 指定店铺。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091332Xo9Ik4HOYwsfi7B1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609090913483JnqLgRFuk4X61NW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091348TOXNB5dsKDUlu3gE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160909091353m5ydM0C246ArRHGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609090914021SAxobVEBGuCFOnN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}